skins.selfIntroduction: I'm the Type-B class cruiser submarine, I-25. I'm at my best when it comes to reconnaissance and disrupting shipping routes. I've also been in some... pretty daring operations. Hehe~ Commander, you can count on me.
skins.acquisition: Phew... I finally found you! Commander, I'm I-25. I hope that I can be a big help to you. Anyway, it's nice meeting you~
skins.login: Mmh... Welcome back, Commander. While you were gone, I finished compiling all the reports. Here you go~
skins.details: Sorry to bother you when you're busy, Commander, but could you please help me test the capabilities of my seaplane?
skins.secretaryIdle1: Where I'm from, we always offer our respects for the food in front of us before each meal. It's a custom that helps us be at ease.
skins.secretaryIdle2: I hope my sister hasn't been causing too much trouble for you. She's a little ball of energy... there's no way I can keep up with her...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Commander... Commander...? Are you still asleep? I'm getting a bit worried...
skins.secretaryTouch: Haah... I'm being filled to the brim with your energy, Commander...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Commander, do you... like this kind of sensation...?

skins.shipDescription: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?
skins.acquisition: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?
skins.login: D-deep sea fish, attack! Umm, uh... that's not how it works...? I don't seem to be very good at this...
skins.details: Which subjects am I good at? I'd say I'm pretty decent at all of them. Ehehe, I did say you can leave everything to me.
skins.secretaryIdle1: Coral reefs are breathtakingly beautiful, Commander. If you ever want to see for yourself, just let me know.
skins.secretaryIdle2: This might sound strange coming from me, but forest fires are a very serious matter. There will be dire consequences if you don't take that to heart. Just ask the girls of the Eagle Union.
skins.secretaryIdle3: There's nothing wrong with I-19, right... The next time I-26 calls everyone to play, I'll go check on her.
skins.secretaryTouch: Haah... as long as you're by my side, I feel safe and sound.
